name: interview-master
description: ## Submission Guidelines: * Of the roles linked to, choose the one that best aligns with your skillset and desired role at mySidewalk. * Read the prompt and prepare a submission that satisfies its requirements. * Include all source code, configuration, tests, assets, and documentation. * Archive (zip, 7z, gztar, etc.) your program and all supporting materials. * Email your submission to careers@mysidewalk.com, subject line: “Code Submission: [Insert Role]”.
author: Adam Bungart
